edit: oh it should be noted that the distribution of spells is not even, just as it is for all weapons. <br>
as always, the people at &quot;the top&quot; will get them first (in big guilds, or with alot of plat), then once that market is sated, whats left will trickle down to the rest of the players for a lower value.<br>
if (guessing here) 10 &quot;uber&quot; monk useable weapons enter the world every day, that doesnt necessarily mean they will be evenly distributed through the players. some will rot (because no guild monks will need), and the rest will go to the &quot;uber&quot; monks, or if tradeable will be sold. <br>
